Æ6¶U<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";s:776:"<p>Tara holds full registration with the Australian Health Practitioner Regulation Agency with endorsement as a Clinical Psychologist, and is recognised by Medicare as a provider of clinical psychology services. She uses a variety of approaches including Cognitive Behavioural Therapy, Acceptance and Commitment Therapy, Schema Therapy, and Narrative Therapy. Tara focuses on building warm, comfortable and collaborative relationships with clients to support them to achieve their goals. She also considers humour and fun to be an important part of the therapy process. Tara has a particular research interest in the adjustment and coping of parents of premature infants. In her spare time she enjoys having fun and keeping active with her young child and boisterous dogs.</p>";}